## 🚀 Setup & Deployment

### 🔗 Google Sheets Integration
1. Set up a **Google Apps Script** project linked to your target Google Sheet.
2. Deploy the script as a web app.
3. Update your JS `fetch()` URL to point to the deployment endpoint.

### 🌐 Deployment Options
- ✅ **GitHub Pages**
- ✅ **Google Drive public hosting (basic static hosting)**
- ❌ Database no longer required in `v1.2`

